    "title": "Sherehe",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "sherehe",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu anapokea kwa furaha na shangwe maonyesho ya ibada na sifa kutoka kwa wale wanaomwabudu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:29\">Isaya 30:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:19\">Yeremia 30:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:13\">31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:17\">Sefania 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:19\">Waefeso 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">Wakolosai 3:16</a>).</p><p>Mfalme Daudi alijaribu mara mbili kuleta sanduku la Mungu (pia linaitwa &quot;sanduku la Bwana&quot; au &quot;Sanduku la Agano&quot;) hadi Yerusalemu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:1-2Sam6:11\">2 Samweli 6:1–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:12-2Sam6:23\">12–23</a>). Kila jaribio lilihusisha sherehe.</p><p>Kwenye maandamano ya Pili na sanduku, maneno matatu ya Kiebrania yanaelezea &quot;kucheza&quot; (tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:25-1Chr15:29\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 15:25–29</a>):</p><ol><li><p><em>karar</em> (&quot;Alikuwa akicheza&quot; katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:14\">2 Samweli 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:16\">16</a>)</p></li><li><p><em>pazaz</em> (&quot;kuruka&quot; katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:16\">2 Samweli 6:16</a>)</p></li><li><p><em>Raqad</em> (&quot;kusherehekea&quot; katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:29\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 15:29</a>)</p></li></ol><p>Maneno haya yanaonyesha maonyesho ya mwili yenye uhai, tofauti na neno la Kiebrania kwa &quot;sherehekea&quot; lililotumiwa katika jaribio la kwanza la Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:5\">2 Samweli 6:5</a>). Katika maandamano ya kwanza na sanduku, Daudi alisherehekea. Katika ya pili, alicheza kwa furaha na kusherehekea kwa muziki, kupiga kelele, na tarumbeta.</p><p>Vyombo vya muziki vilikuwa muhimu katika ibada ya hekalu. Katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:1-1Chr25:31\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 25:1–31</a>, Daudi aliteua vikundi kwa ajili ya huduma ya muziki. Zaburi nyingi zinataja kucheza vyombo ili kumsifu na kumwabudu Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:2-Ps33:3\">Zaburi 33:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:8\">57:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:2\">81:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:1-Ps92:3\">92:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:4-Ps98:6\">98:4–6</a>). Katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:1-Ps149:9\">Zaburi 149</a> na <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:1-Ps150:6\">150</a>, dansi na muziki vinachanganywa kama sadaka ya sifa. Vivyo hivyo, muziki na dansi vilikuwepo katika nyumba ya Baba katika mfano wa mwana mpotevu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:25\">Luka 15:25</a>). Hii ilikuwa kwa sababu kurudi kwa mwana ilikuwa tukio la furaha.</p><p>Kitabu cha Ufunuo kinaelezea sherehe ya milele kwa waaminifu. Sherehe hii inajumuisha ibada mbele ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:1-Rev4:11\">Ufunuo 4:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8-Rev5:14\">5:8–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:1-Rev15:4\">15:1–4</a>). Ni kama karamu ya harusi ambapo bwana arusi (Yesu Kristo) na bibi arusi (kanisa lake) wanaungana milele (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:9\">Ufunuo 19:9</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:1-Matt22:14\">Mathayo 22:1–14</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:1\">Kutoka 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:17\">12:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20-Exod15:21\">15:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:6\">1 Samweli 18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:1-2Sam6:15\">2 Samweli 6:1–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:6-2Chr7:10\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 7:6–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10-Ezra3:11\">Ezra 3:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:11\">Zaburi 30:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30\">69:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:4-Ps98:6\">98:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:32\">107:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:1-Ps149:9\">149:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:1-Ps150:6\">150:1–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:29\">Isaya 30:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:1\">54:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18-Jer30:19\">Yeremia 30:18–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:4\">31:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:13\">13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:14-Lam5:15\">Maombolezo 5:14–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:17\">Sefania 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:22-Luke15:25\">Luka 15:22–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:8\">1 Wakorintho 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18-Eph5:20\">Waefeso 5:18–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">Wakolosai 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:20\">Ufunuo 18:20</a></p>",
